            Optimize your thermostat settings. Every degree adjustment can lead
            to significant energy savings over time.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-card">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-power-off"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Standby Power</h3>
          <p>
            Eliminate phantom energy usage by unplugging devices when not in use
            or using smart power strips.
          </p>
        </div>
